Hospitality Analysis Dashboard
This project includes an interactive Power BI Dashboard that transforms raw hotel data into actionable business insights.

Key Features:

Pricing Insights: Visualizes price distributions across different city markets.
Hotel Segmentation: Categorizes hotels into Budget, Mid-range, and Luxury bands.
Performance Metrics: Analyzes the relationship between average ratings, discount percentages, and pricing.
Geographic Analysis: Compares hotel availability and costs across major Indian cities.
Interactive Filters: Allows users to filter data by city and rating to find the best value-for-money options.

Tools Used:
Power BI: For data modeling and visualization.
DAX: Used to create custom measures and calculated columns.
